subject: Attention:Beneficiary,
body:
Attention:Beneficiary,

Kindly specify the following below:
FULL NAME:

subject: Re: Attention:Beneficiary,
body:
Dear Mr. Philip Brown,

I'm afraid there seems to be some confusion. I have not received any payment nor was I expecting one. Could you please provide more details about this supposed transaction?

Best wishes,
Tara
